      "rationale": "The normalised index of hemolysis and relative hemolysis index are the primary regulatory QoIs for CPB device assessment. Both are computed by the post-processing hemolysis integration module using the power-law damage accumulation model (Giersiepen et al.). The QoIs map directly to the RH < 1 acceptance criterion. Achieved level 2 meets the requirement."
