      "rationale": "All validation activities (VR-01 through VR-04) were conducted using the FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry at CPB-representative flow rates (2–6 L/min) and rotational speeds (2000–3500 RPM). The validation domain closely matches the COU. Achieved level 2 meets the requirement."
